# Navigation Flow Diagram

```mermaid
graph TD
    START[Start] --> GET[Get Waypoint]
    GET --> PLAN[Plan Path]
    PLAN --> EXEC[Execute Movement]
    EXEC --> SCAN[Scan for Obstacles]
    SCAN --> CHECK{Clear?}
    CHECK -->|Yes| ARRIVE{At Waypoint?}
    CHECK -->|No| REPLAN[Replan Path]
    REPLAN --> EXEC
    ARRIVE -->|No| EXEC
    ARRIVE -->|Yes| END[End]
```
